definitions.definition: A thing or quality that has value , especially one that generates cash flows.
examples: My assets consist of stocks in companies that pay a dividend, and a few apartments that pay me rental income.

subdefinitions.definition: Any item recorded on the left-hand side of a balance sheet .

definitions.definition: Any component , model , process or framework of value that can be leveraged or reused .
A woman's breasts or buttocks or a man's genitalia .
